			</p>
			<form id="shortenForm">
				<div class="flex flex-col gap-1 mt-9">
					<textarea class="w-full p-2 rounded bg-slate-800 text-gray-300 focus:outline-none border border-slate-600 placeholder:text-gray-400" type="url" id="url_origin" name="url_origin" placeholder="Enter your url ..." required></textarea>
					<div class="flex justify-center mt-6">
						<button class="bg-blue-700 hover:bg-blue-600 px-4 py-2 text-gray-100 rounded-md" type="submit">Generate</button>
					</div>
				</div>
			</form>
